---
import acornWordmark from './public/acorn-wordmark.png';
---
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Acorn | Sovereign AI for 7-Figure Founders</title>
        <script is:inline>
            document.documentElement.classList.add('is-loaded');
        </script>
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=EB+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="site-header">
            <div class="shell nav-inner">
                <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="Acorn home">
                    <img src={acornWordmark.src} alt="Acorn Rooted Intelligence" />
                </a>

                <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-btn">Join Waitlist</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="shell hero-inner">
                    <p class="eyebrow">ROOTED INTELLIGENCE</p>
                    <h1>Does your AI work for you?</h1>
                    <p class="hero-sub">Acorn is a business-first AI operating system that lives in Slack, and is loyal to you, not big tech.</p>
                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <a href="#waitlist" class="btn-primary">Join the Acorn Waitlist</a>
                        <a href="#orientation-protocol" class="btn-secondary">Read the Orientation Protocol</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="metric-strip" aria-label="Acorn operating system attributes">
                        <div><span>Private Memory</span><strong>Your cloud</strong></div>
                        <div><span>Interface</span><strong>Slack-native</strong></div>
                        <div><span>Execution</span><strong>You approve actions</strong></div>
                        <div><span>Context</span><strong>You choose what it sees</strong></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-wave" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </section>

            <section class="control-context section-pad">
                <div class="shell cc-grid">
                    <article class="need-card need-card-light">
                        <p class="eyebrow">SOVEREIGNTY</p>
                        <h2>You Need Control.</h2>
                        <p>Your data is yours. Acorn runs in your cloud, on your terms. No co-mingling, no model training on your private conversations, and no hidden dependency on someone else's memory.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="need-card need-card-dark">
                        <p class="eyebrow">INTELLIGENCE LAYER</p>
                        <h2>You Need Context.</h2>
                        <p>Acorn reads what you allow it to read: Slack, Drive, Notion, email. It builds a private operating picture of your business, learning your team, projects, standards, and voice.</p>
                        <span class="status-pill">Unified Intelligence</span>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="context-map section-pad">
                <div class="shell map-grid">
                    <div class="map-copy">
                        <p class="eyebrow">PRIVATE CONTEXT ARCHITECTURE</p>
                        <h2>Acorn only sees what you allow.</h2>
                        <p>Connect the systems that already carry your business context. Acorn turns those signals into private operating memory, then routes the right work back into your team rhythm.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="map-card" aria-label="Context architecture diagram">
                        <div class="source-list">
                            <span>Slack</span>
                            <span>Drive</span>
                            <span>Notion</span>
                            <span>Email</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="map-core">
                            <span class="core-ring"></span>
                            <strong>Acorn</strong>
                            <small>Private Business Context</small>
                        </div>
                        <div class="output-list">
                            <span>Oriented Decisions</span>
                            <span>Context-Aware Drafts</span>
                            <span>Prioritized Follow-ups</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="orientation section-pad">
                <div class="shell editorial-card">
                    <div class="orient-copy">
                        <p class="eyebrow">THE FRAMEWORK</p>
                        <h2>Orientation beats delegation.</h2>
                        <p>Most people use AI to delegate tasks: faster email, faster docs, faster noise. Acorn is different. It uses the OODA loop to understand your terrain before it acts, so execution stays connected to judgment.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ooda-grid" aria-label="OODA loop">
                        <div class="ooda-step">Observe</div>
                        <div class="ooda-step active">Orient</div>
                        <div class="ooda-step">Decide</div>
                        <div class="ooda-step">Act</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="meet-acorn section-pad">
                <div class="shell meet-grid">
                    <div class="meet-copy">
                        <p class="eyebrow">AGENTIC AI ARCHITECTURE</p>
                        <h2>Meet Acorn</h2>
                        <p>A Chief of Staff agent that lives in your cloud, talks to you in Slack, and earns your trust over time.</p>
                        <div class="feature-row">
                            <span class="feature-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Lives in your cloud</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-row">
                            <span class="feature-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Slack interface</span>
                        </div>
                        <button class="demo-replay" type="button" aria-controls="acorn-demo">Replay demo</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="slack-card" id="acorn-demo" aria-label="Acorn Slack-style conversation">
                        <div class="slack-top">
                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                            <strong># founder-ops</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div class="status-stack">
                            <span>Reading Q2 targets</span>
                            <span>Cross-checking Martinez call</span>
                            <span>Draft ready</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chat-bubble user-bubble">What's our top priority this week?</div>
                        <div class="chat-bubble acorn-bubble">Based on your Q2 targets and yesterday's client call with Martinez, closing the proposal revision is the highest-leverage move. Want me to draft the updated scope?</div>
                        <div class="trust-badge">Trust mode: Propose and Wait</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="sovereignty-band">
                <div class="shell sovereignty-inner">
                    <div>
                        <p class="eyebrow">SOVEREIGN AI INFRASTRUCTURE</p>
                        <h2>Leverage without surrendering control.</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="security-claims">
                        <span>Runs in your cloud</span>
                        <span>No training on private data</span>
                        <span>Permissioned memory only</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="trust section-pad">
                <div class="shell trust-inner">
                    <p class="eyebrow">THE TRUST GRADIENT</p>
                    <h2>How Trust Is Earned</h2>
                    <p class="trust-sub">Acorn wins your trust through performance and never oversteps.</p>
                    <div class="trust-grid">
                        <article class="trust-card">
                            <span class="icon-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <h3>Act and Report</h3>
                            <p>For routine tasks within its authority, Acorn acts first and tells you what it did. No bottleneck. No waiting.</p>
                        </article>
                        <article class="trust-card featured">
                            <span class="card-pill">DEFAULT STATE</span>
                            <span class="icon-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <h3>Propose and Wait</h3>
                            <p>For decisions that need your judgment, Acorn presents options and waits for your call. It never overreaches.</p>
                        </article>
                        <article class="trust-card">
                            <span class="icon-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <h3>Escalate</h3>
                            <p>When something falls outside its scope, Acorn flags it immediately. No guessing. No pretending to know.</p>
                        </article>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="why-acorn section-pad">
                <div class="shell vision-card">
                    <p class="eyebrow">FOUNDER'S VISION</p>
                    <h2>Why Acorn</h2>
                    <blockquote>"The 7-figure business owner is the most underserved person in AI. Enterprise gets custom builds. Consumers get ChatGPT. The founder running a real business with real employees and real risk? Nobody is building for them. Until now."</blockquote>
                    <p class="attribution">Brian Keith, Founder</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="protocol section-pad" id="orientation-protocol">
                <div class="shell protocol-grid">
                    <div>
                        <p class="eyebrow">FOUNDER RESOURCE</p>
                        <h2>Download the Orientation Protocol</h2>
                        <p>Not ready for the waitlist? Use the Orientation Protocol to start giving your current AI tools better context on your judgment, risk tolerance, and values.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="protocol-preview">
                        <div class="pdf-card" aria-label="Orientation Protocol PDF preview">
                            <span class="pdf-kicker">ACORN DOCTRINE</span>
                            <h3>Orientation Protocol</h3>
                            <div class="pdf-lines">
                                <span></span><span></span><span></span>
                            </div>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Judgment map</li>
                                <li>Risk tolerances</li>
                                <li>Values and constraints</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <form class="protocol-form">
                            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required />
                            <button class="btn-secondary" type="submit">Download Orientation Protocol PDF</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="waitlist-wrap section-pad" id="waitlist">
                <div class="waitlist-card">
                    <p class="eyebrow">GET EARLY ACCESS</p>
                    <h2>Join the Acorn Waitlist</h2>
                    <p class="waitlist-sub">Deploy a sovereign AI system built for your business. Limited early access.</p>
                    <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/app/form/process/8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" class="infusion-form waitlist-form" id="inf_form_8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" method="POST">
                        <input name="inf_form_xid" type="hidden" value="8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" />
                        <input name="inf_thank_you" type="hidden" value="https://buyacorn.com/welcome.html/" />
                        <input name="inf_form_name" type="hidden" value="BuyAcorn.com Waitlist" />
                        <input name="infusionsoft_version" type="hidden" value="1.70.0.942760" />
                        <input id="inf_field_Email" name="inf_field_Email" placeholder="Enter your email" type="email" required />
                        <button class="btn-primary infusion-recaptcha" id="recaptcha_8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba" type="submit">Join Acorn Waitlist</button>
                        <input type="text" name="inf-sbt" style="display:none !important;" />
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer class="site-footer">
            <div class="shell footer-inner">
                <a href="/" class="footer-logo" aria-label="Acorn home">
                    <img src={acornWordmark.src} alt="Acorn Rooted Intelligence" />
                </a>
                <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Red Beard Consulting LLC. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </footer>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.app/app/webTracking/getTrackingCode"></script>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/resources/external/recaptcha/production/recaptcha.js?b=1.70.0.942760"></script>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/resources/external/recaptcha/production/enterpriseRecaptcha.js?b=1.70.0.942760"></script>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/app/timezone/timezoneInputJs?xid=8bce157b4a83074b0edda9c55e1ed0ba"></script>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.com/js/jquery/jquery-3.3.1.js"></script>
        <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://redbeard.infusionsoft.app/app/webform/overwriteRefererJs"></script>
        <script is:inline>
            document.querySelectorAll('form').forEach((form) => {
                form.addEventListener('submit', () => {
                    form.classList.add('is-submitting');
                    const button = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
                    if (button) {
                        button.dataset.label = button.textContent || '';
                        button.textContent = 'Securing request...';
                    }
                });
            });

            const demoButton = document.querySelector('.demo-replay');
            const acornDemo = document.getElementById('acorn-demo');

            if (demoButton && acornDemo) {
                const replayDemo = () => {
                    acornDemo.classList.remove('is-replaying');
                    void acornDemo.offsetWidth;
                    acornDemo.classList.add('is-replaying');
                };

                demoButton.addEventListener('click', replayDemo);
                window.setTimeout(replayDemo, 900);
            }
        </script>
    </body>
</html>

<style>
    :root {
        --rooted-green: #0A3D2F;
        --signal-sage: #8FA89A;
        --oak-brown: #5C4B43;
        --paper-white: #F5F2EB;
        --paper-deep: #ECE6D9;
        --tech-grey: #333333;
        --muted: #615D55;
        --border: #DED8CA;
        --white: #FFFFFF;
        --font-serif: 'EB Garamond', Georgia, serif;
        --font-sans: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
        background: var(--paper-white);
        color: var(--tech-grey);
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .hero-inner > *,
    .need-card,
    .map-copy,
    .map-card,
    .editorial-card,
    .meet-copy,
    .slack-card,
    .sovereignty-inner > *,
    .trust-inner > *,
    .vision-card,
    .protocol-grid > *,
    .waitlist-card {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(18px);
    }

    .is-loaded .hero-inner > *,
    .is-loaded .need-card,
    .is-loaded .map-copy,
    .is-loaded .map-card,
    .is-loaded .editorial-card,
    .is-loaded .meet-copy,
    .is-loaded .slack-card,
    .is-loaded .sovereignty-inner > *,
    .is-loaded .trust-inner > *,
    .is-loaded .vision-card,
    .is-loaded .protocol-grid > *,
    .is-loaded .waitlist-card {
        animation: reveal-up 720ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) forwards;
    }

    .is-loaded .hero-inner > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 80ms; }
    .is-loaded .hero-inner > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 150ms; }
    .is-loaded .hero-inner > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 220ms; }
    .is-loaded .hero-inner > *:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 300ms; }

    img {
        max-width: 100%;
    }

    .shell {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 48px));
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-pad {
        padding: 88px 0;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3 {
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--rooted-green);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 82px);
        line-height: 0.98;
        max-width: 880px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 56px);
        line-height: 1.05;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    p {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .eyebrow {
        color: var(--signal-sage);
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .site-header,
    .site-footer {
        background: var(--rooted-green);
        border-color: transparent;
    }

    .site-header {
        border-bottom: none;
        padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .nav-inner,
    .footer-inner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .nav-logo,
    .footer-logo {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-logo img,
    .footer-logo img {
        display: block;
        height: auto;
        width: 158px;
    }

    .nav-btn,
    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
        align-items: center;
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: inline-flex;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 48px;
        padding: 14px 22px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 180ms ease, border-color 180ms ease, color 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .nav-btn,
    .btn-primary {
        background: var(--rooted-green);
        border: 1px solid var(--rooted-green);
        color: var(--white);
    }

    .site-header .nav-btn {
        background: var(--white);
        border-color: var(--white);
        color: var(--rooted-green);
    }

    .nav-btn:hover,
    .nav-btn:focus-visible,
    .btn-primary:hover,
    .btn-primary:focus-visible {
        background: #083329;
        border-color: #083329;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(10, 61, 47, 0.26);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .site-header .nav-btn:hover,
    .site-header .nav-btn:focus-visible {
        background: var(--paper-white);
        border-color: var(--paper-white);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
        color: var(--rooted-green);
    }

    .nav-btn:active,
    .btn-primary:active,
    .btn-secondary:active {
        transform: translateY(0) scale(0.98);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
        border: 1px solid rgba(92, 75, 67, 0.24);
        color: var(--rooted-green);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover,
    .btn-secondary:focus-visible {
        background: var(--white);
        border-color: var(--rooted-green);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.12);
        transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .hero {
        background:
            linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(10, 61, 47, 0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
            radial-gradient(circle at 15% 18%, rgba(143, 168, 154, 0.16), transparent 28%),
            var(--paper-white);
        background-size: 42px 42px, auto, auto;
        min-height: 680px;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 118px 0 138px;
        position: relative;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-inner {
        align-items: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-sub {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 19px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin: 28px auto 38px;
        max-width: 720px;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 14px;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .metric-strip {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
        border: 1px solid rgba(92, 75, 67, 0.16);
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
        margin-top: 54px;
        max-width: 860px;
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .metric-strip div {
        border-right: 1px solid rgba(92, 75, 67, 0.14);
        cursor: default;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        text-align: left;
        transition: background 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
    }

    .metric-strip div:hover {
        background: var(--white);
        box-shadow: inset 0 3px 0 var(--rooted-green), 0 20px 38px rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.12);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .metric-strip div:last-child {
        border-right: none;
    }

    .metric-strip span {
        color: var(--oak-brown);
        display: block;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .metric-strip strong {
        color: var(--rooted-green);
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hero-wave {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(245, 242, 235, 0), var(--paper-white) 72%);
        border-radius: 48% 52% 0 0 / 70% 62% 0 0;
        bottom: -92px;
        height: 180px;
        left: -5%;
        position: absolute;
        right: -5%;
    }

    .cc-grid,
    .meet-grid,
    .protocol-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 28px;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .need-card,
    .editorial-card,
    .slack-card,
    .vision-card,
    .waitlist-card,
    .card-surface {
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.12);
    }

    .need-card,
    .editorial-card,
    .slack-card,
    .vision-card,
    .waitlist-card,
    .pdf-card {
        transition: background 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease, box-shadow 160ms ease, transform 160ms ease;
    }

    .need-card:hover,
    .editorial-card:hover,
    .slack-card:hover,
    .vision-card:hover,
    .waitlist-card:hover,
    .pdf-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(92, 75, 67, 0.28);
        box-shadow: 0 38px 96px rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.18);
        transform: translateY(-7px);
    }

    .need-card {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        min-height: 360px;
        padding: 44px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .need-card-light {
        background: var(--white);
    }

    .need-card-dark {
        background: var(--rooted-green);
        border-color: var(--rooted-green);
    }

    .need-card-dark h2,
    .need-card-dark p {
        color: var(--white);
    }

    .need-card-dark p {
        opacity: 0.86;
    }

    .status-pill,
    .card-pill {
        border-radius: 999px;
        display: inline-flex;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .status-pill {
        background: rgba(143, 168, 154, 0.18);
        bottom: 34px;
        color: var(--white);
        position: absolute;
    }

    .context-map {
        background: var(--paper-white);
        padding-top: 24px;
    }

    .map-grid {
        align-items: center;
        display: grid;
        gap: 42px;
        grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
    }

    .map-copy p:last-child {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .map-card {
        background:
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(10, 61, 47, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
            linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(10, 61, 47, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
            var(--white);
        background-size: 34px 34px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(51, 51, 51, 0.12);
        display: grid;
        gap: 24px;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr 1fr;
        min-height: 340px;
        padding: 34px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .source-list,
    .output-list {
        display: flex;
